a problem making up your mind.

55
00:03:19,661 --> 00:03:21,781
No, I've decided.
I'll take it. Yokoi.

56
00:03:23,591 --> 00:03:25,821
- Wait a minute!
- I'm not waiting.

57
00:03:25,961 --> 00:03:29,001
I'm tired of staying
at crappy capsule hotels.

58
00:03:29,001 --> 00:03:31,701
