67
00:03:48,591 --> 00:03:50,691
Now, come on.
Rather than discussing nonsense,

68
00:03:50,691 --> 00:03:52,311
what are you gonna do
about renting this...

69
00:03:52,391 --> 00:03:53,581
- Nonsense?
- Nonsense?

70
00:03:54,091 --> 00:03:56,561
How cruel!
Here I am seriously suffering!

71
00:03:56,561 --> 00:03:57,751
- Yokoi!
- Yes!

72
00:03:57,931 --> 00:03:59,661
For someone in the business
of serving customers,

73
00:03:59,661 --> 00:04:01,561
you've got no delicacy!

74
00:04:01,671 --> 00:04:02,831
I-I'm sorry.

75
00:04:02,931 --> 00:04:05,601
There's more to doing your job
than just go through the motions!

76
00:04:05,601 --> 00:04:06,701
Try to pursue the romance!

77
00:04:06,701 --> 00:04:09,431
Now, now. Calm down, ladies.

78
00:04:09,611 --> 00:04:10,231
Romance?

79
00:04:10,911 --> 00:04:13,601
I have a suggestion.

80
00:04:13,881 --> 00:04:16,281
Who is this carefree old man?

81
00:04:16,411 --> 00:04:18,941
This is Mr. Ando from
the real estate agency at the train station.

82
00:04:19,481 --> 00:04:22,381
He's a 52-year veteran in this business.

83
00:04:22,791 --> 00:04:26,191
You two seem to be
special acquaintances.

84
00:04:26,561 --> 00:04:29,321
Why don't the two of you
share this place?

85
00:04:30,261 --> 00:04:33,901
This place is designed with
the dining room in the middle,

86
00:04:33,901 --> 00:04:36,461
so with a room on opposite sides,
you can maintain your privacy.

87
00:04:37,371 --> 00:04:39,961
Yet you'll be there for
each other when needed.

88
00:04:40,401 --> 00:04:43,241
Flat-sharing can be very nice.

89
00:04:44,011 --> 00:04:47,501
Plus, you'll only be paying half the rent
and living expenses.

90
00:04:47,611 --> 00:04:49,171
- Half the rent?!
- Half the rent?!

91
00:04:49,581 --> 00:04:51,481
- Half of 70,000 yen is...
...35,000 yen?

92
00:04:51,881 --> 00:04:53,111
- That's cheap!
- That's cheap!

93
00:04:53,881 --> 00:04:55,391
Let's go for it, Nana!

94
00:04:55,391 --> 00:04:57,591
- It's like a dream to be able to stay...
- Then we'll have to split our fees, too.

95
00:04:57,591 --> 00:04:59,051
at such a wonderful place
for so cheap!

96
00:04:59,221 --> 00:05:00,291
Sounds good,

97
00:05:00,291 --> 00:05:03,261
but are you the kind of person who
properly respects the privacy of others?

98
00:05:03,591 --> 00:05:05,321
I will! For sure!

99
00:05:05,831 --> 00:05:11,131
If privacy is an issue,
you can put locks on your room doors.

100
00:05:11,601 --> 00:05:13,661
I'll arrange for that right away.

101
00:05:14,401 --> 00:05:15,971
Thank you, Mr. Ando!

102
00:05:15,971 --> 00:05:17,471
You are such a nice person.
Isn't he, Nana?

103
00:05:17,471 --> 00:05:21,341
