sometime tomorrow morning.

110
00:05:42,631 --> 00:05:46,531
Then please.
I'll be moving in tomorrow afternoon.

111
00:05:48,811 --> 00:05:49,401
What about you?

112
00:05:52,511 --> 00:05:53,641
Th-Then me too.

113
00:06:02,221 --> 00:06:04,591
