about breaking up with her, is he?

212
00:11:33,851 --> 00:11:37,791
No, the opposite.
He wants to marry Nana.

213
00:11:38,561 --> 00:11:41,581
Marry?! Is he outta his mind?!
They're only twenty!

214
00:11:41,861 --> 00:11:44,451
I don't think he wants
to do it just yet.

215
00:11:45,961 --> 00:11:47,901
