until after that.

217
00:11:51,571 --> 00:11:52,871
So he was wondering
whether or not

218
00:11:52,871 --> 00:11:54,901
he should just quit studying
for the entrance exam

219
00:11:54,901 --> 00:11:56,601
and find a full time job.

220
00:11:57,011 --> 00:11:58,911
Just make her wait.

221
00:11:59,311 --> 00:12:02,571
